data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This beautifully designed one-level residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and privacy. Located in a peaceful neighborhood, this property boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a serene covered back patio that provides the ideal space for relaxation and entertaining. From the moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the relaxed flow of the ranch style home. The spacious living area, accentuated by the electric fireplace, is the perfect spot to create lasting memories with loved ones. Retreat to the generously-sized bedrooms, offering comfort and privacy for everyone in the household. The VIP bedroom boasts a pocket door leading to an ensuite bathroom with walk-in shower for added convenience. Step outside to the enchanting covered back patio, surrounded by lush greenery and designed to be your private sanctuary. Whether you're savoring your morning coffee or hosting a BBQ with friends, this space is sure to become your favorite spot to unwind. The property's oversized 2-car garage, with laundry area, not only provides secure parking but also offers additional storage solutions, keeping your home organized and clutter-free. With a location that balances tranquility with accessibility, you'll find yourself conveniently located to schools, parks, shopping, restaurants, and major transportation routes. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a home that checks all the boxes! Schedule a viewing today and make this remarkable property your forever home. Home warranty included.
